data.description: **TRULY A CUSTOM-BUILT HOME**EXTREMLY RARE FIND IN DOLAN SPRINGS** This Modern Beauty Still Shows Like A Model Home** Built-in 2016 & Positioned to View all the Mountains around Us** Quality & Comfort Meet Here Making This Dream Of Living In Arizona s High Desert A Reality. Excellent Design Features Paired with Over-the-Top Workmanship to Create this Site-Built Masterpiece** Come Enjoy A Lifestyle that Includes Privacy & Pleasure** Wild Life Retreat Everywhere You Look** Situated in the Most Desired Location in Dolan Springs** Open Floor Plan allowing Lots of natural Light to shine through the home, This Stucco Exterior, 3 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms, Master features Walk-in closet & Bathroom, Cute Kitchen & Modern Cabinets & Counter Tops, Indoor Laundry, Tiled Floors, Power & Septic System all in place, Town Water Supplied (no water hauling), Central Heating & Air, Attached Garage with extra storage area, Appliances are Staying, Covered RV Parking, Property is Fenced & Gated, Backyard which is large enough for entertaining & still room for all your animal & livestock companions, Close to paved Pierce Ferry road, Property is on a County Graded Road, Minutes to Hwy 93 & Downtown Dolan Springs for all your daily needs, LOOK NO FURTHER! THIS ONE CHECKS ALL THE BOXES ON YOUR DREAM CHECKLIST. Amazing chance to own your own High desert Property. !!!   If you enjoy boating, fishing, hiking, swimming, camping, or any outdoor fun activities, this is the place for you. Endless miles of quad trails. Taxes are low and NO HOA TO MAINTAIN. The weather is mild all year around and the air is clean. Enjoy crisp clear star-studded skies. You will not be disappointed with this simple beautiful Southwest desert retreat. Dolan Springs is a gateway to the Grand Canyon Skywalk. It is close to Vegas, Laughlin, and Kingman. Night skies are clear and star-studded. It is an excellent choice for relocation or a weekend getaway from crowded city living. Come grab a piece of our beautiful desert and Joshua tree forest area. You won't be disappointed.
